.TH "HPC\-COMPOSE\-GERMINATE" "1" "" "hpc\-compose 0.1.42" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
hpc\-compose\-germinate \- Submit a short canary run and recommend resource settings
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
hpc\-compose germinate [OPTIONS]
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Submit a minimized Slurm canary allocation, force metrics sampling on, wait for it to finish, then compare observed usage against the original compose request and print right\-sizing recommendations.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB-f\fR, \fB--file\fR \fIFILE\fR
Compose specification file to read; if omitted, use the active context compose file or fall back to compose.yaml.
.TP
\fB--script\-out\fR \fIOUTPUT\fR
Write the rendered canary script to this path before submission.
.TP
\fB--canary\-time\fR \fITIME\fR
Walltime for the canary allocation. Default: 00:01:00.
.TP
\fB--metrics\-interval\fR \fISECONDS\fR
Metrics sampler interval forced into the canary plan. Default: 5.
.TP
\fB--pending\-timeout\fR \fIDURATION\fR
Give up if the canary remains non\-terminal for this long. Default: 30m.
.TP
\fB--min\-cpus\fR \fICPUS\fR
Minimum canary CPUs per task. Default: 1.
.TP
\fB--min\-mem\fR \fIMEM\fR
Minimum canary memory. Default: 1G.
.TP
\fB--min\-gpus\fR \fIGPUS\fR
Minimum canary GPU count when the original plan requests GPUs. Default: 1.
.TP
\fB--sbatch\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the sbatch executable. Default: sbatch.
.TP
\fB--srun\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the srun executable. Default: srun.
.TP
\fB--squeue\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the squeue executable. Default: squeue.
.TP
\fB--sacct\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the sacct executable. Default: sacct.
.TP
\fB--sstat\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the sstat executable. Default: sstat.
.TP
\fB--enroot\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the enroot executable. Default: enroot.
.TP
\fB--apptainer\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the apptainer executable. Default: apptainer.
.TP
\fB--singularity\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the singularity executable. Default: singularity.
.TP
\fB--keep\-failed\-prep\fR
Keep failed preparation state on disk for later inspection.
.TP
\fB--skip\-prepare\fR
Skip image preparation and reuse existing artifacts.
.TP
\fB--force\-rebuild\fR
Refresh imported and prepared artifacts before submission.
.TP
\fB--no\-preflight\fR
Skip the preflight phase before submission.
.TP
\fB--dry\-run\fR
Render the canary script without submitting it.
.TP
\fB--format\fR \fIFORMAT\fR
Output format. Possible values: text, json.
.TP
\fB--color\fR \fIWHEN\fR
Controls colored output. Default: auto. Possible values: auto, always, never.
.TP
\fB--quiet\fR
Suppress progress indicators and non\-essential labels.
.TP
\fB--profile\fR \fINAME\fR
Profile name to load from .hpc\-compose/settings.toml.
.TP
\fB--settings\-file\fR \fIPATH\fR
Explicit settings file path; defaults to upward search for .hpc\-compose/settings.toml.
.TP
\fB-h\fR, \fB--help\fR
Print help (see a summary with '\-h').
